title: 5 Bed 4 Bath Home for Rent in Maple Plain, MN
posting_body: ['7805 Deer Creek Circle, Maple Plain, MN, 55359', 'Your Next Place is excited to partner with this landlord to help market 7805 Deer Creek Circle in Maple Plain.', 'This stunning home is located on over 4 acres right in the middle of Minnetrista at the end of a cul-de-sac on a fully recreational lake for ultimate privacy, yet still only 35 minutes from Minneapolis.', 'This 5 bedroom 4 bathroom home was built in 1975 and features over 4,100 square feet of furnished living space.', 'Outside you can sit back and relax lakeside by the cozy built-in fire pit and enjoy some outdoor games in the lush grass.', "Inside you'll be greeted by an incredible rock-covered, wood-burning fireplace.", 'The home features high vaulted wood-beamed ceilings and large glass windows that provide relaxing scenic lake views.', 'Cook up a hearty meal at the end of a long day with this large and open kitchen, fully equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a coffee maker, and toaster.', 'On the main level, you will find 3 bedrooms including the master bedroom facing Whaletail Lake with walkthrough full bathroom with double sinks, jacuzzi tub, glass shower stall and a walk-in closet.', 'In the lower level enjoy the large open family room with a flatscreen TV, foosball and pool table perfect for entertaining.', 'There is 4th bedroom is currently a workout room, but can be turned back into a bedroom, with a 5th nonconforming bedroom and one full bathrooom.', 'The large glass windows provide scenic lake views as well as easy access to the side yard.', 'The unique location of Whaletail Lake is perfect for fishing enthusiasts and is minutes from the Lake Minnetonka Chain.', "Just within a few miles of the house are numerous restaurants, breweries and wineries such as Back Channel Brewery, Carbone's, Lord Fletchers, Excelsior Brewing Company, Wayzata Bar and Grill, Maynards Restaurant, Minnetonka Orchard and many more options!", 'This home will be fully furnished, lease term is for a minimum of 6 months.', 'Owner will cover water/sewer, tenant covers remaining utilities (lawn care, snow removal, electric) All can be negotiable as well to be included into rent with slight increase in monthly rate.', 'Pets allowed with an additional deposit and pet rent fee.', '**', 'Available August 1st, 2022.', '**', 'More photos and 360 tour coming
